
Vagrant file to create a VM capable of building the frontend java code.  The current directory (product/frontend) is
rsyn'd to /vagrant on the VM.  Note you cannot run any scripts that try to use perfoce at this time, like
generateServerDocs.sh

Vagrant 101
Check VM status: vagrant status
Bring the VM up: vagrant up
Log into the VM: vagrant ssh
Copy code to VM: vagrant rsync
Remove  the  VM: vagrant destroy
